CBRE is pleased to offer 87 Moreland Street, Footscray, available For Lease.

The property offers an outstanding opportunity to lease in one of Melbourne's highly sought after commercial hubs just off Docklands and only moments to the Melbourne CBD.

Located at 87 Moreland Street, Footscray, this 990sqm* modern office/warehouse has 11 car spaces and a high clearance warehouse with container height roller door.

Positioned moments from Dynon Road and 5km from the CBD and 1.2km* from Footscray Railway Station, this property also provides great access to major arterials such as CityLink.

Property highlights include:
+ Office: 238sqm*
+ Warehouse/showroom: 752sqm*
+ Total building area: 990sqm*
+ 11 on-site car parks
+ Clear span warehouse
+ Air-conditioned office/showroom
+ Modern fit out
+ High clearance

*approx

CBRE is pleased to offer 92 Gordon Street, Footscray, available For Sale by Public Auction, Wednesday 5th July 2017 at 12.30pm on-site.

The property offers an outstanding opportunity to purchase in one of Melbourne's highly sought after commercial hubs.

Located at 92 Gordon Street, Footscray, this 1,890sqm* site comprises a showroom/office/warehouse with an almost 30 metre* frontage.

Positioned just 5km* from Melbourne's CBD, Queen Victoria Market and only 2km* from the Royal Children's Hospital and Footscray Railway Station, this property provides great access to major arterials such as Ballarat Road and City Link.

Features include:
+ Total building area: 1,275sqm*
+ Total land area: 1,890sqm*
+ Almost 30 metre* frontage to Gordon Street
+ Offered with holding income or vacant possession
+ Ideal opportunity to invest and/or develop (STCA)
+ Access to major arterials
+ Includes side drive and rear land
+ Dual roller shutter doors

AUCTION - Wednesday 5th July 2017 at 12.30pm on-site

*approx.
